	                <h4 class="main-title">WHAT IS THE ROLE OF THE INVESTIGATIONS MANAGER?</h4>
	                <p style='margin-left:36.0pt'>Each member of ASIST is assigned to a specific Amazon business format (we call FORMAT FOCUS) and is dedicated to providing advanced investigative assistance to its field LP partners.  By leveraging this partnership, together field LP and ASIST can reduce loss throughout the Network both internally and externally.</p>
