	                <h4 class="main-title">WHEN SHOULD YOU ENGAGE THE TEAM?</h4>
	                <p style='margin-left:36.0pt'>At a high level, ASIST should be leveraged for cases that involve high complexity, severity, sophistication and impact.  However, below are more specific circumstances of when you can utilize the team’s resources.</p>
