	                <h5 class="main-title" style='margin-left:20.0pt'><u>Internal Investigations</u></h5>
	                <p style='margin-left:36.0pt'>	•	Individuals that are working in collusion with each other or with a 3rd party (i.e. contractor, vendor or external subject)<br />
						•	Suspected losses are believed to be greater than $5,000 USD<br />
						•	Subjects are targeting multiple items of the same ASIN or like ASIN’s<br />
						•	Individuals involved in the investigation have over 24 months of employment with the company<br />
						•	Stolen merchandise is being fenced or resold<br />
						•	The removal of merchandise is by means other than through standard egress channels<br />
						•	Investigative intelligence is required<br />
						•	Individuals are involved in sophisticated embedded fraud<br />
						•	The individual holds an elevated or sensitive internal position<br /></p>

